43
00:07:27,301 --> 00:07:28,814
Vai ser apertado.

44
00:07:40,481 --> 00:07:41,953
Olá!

45
00:07:44,026 --> 00:07:45,831
Sacana irrequieto.

46
00:07:49,114 --> 00:07:51,128
Apanhámo-los!

47
00:08:05,214 --> 00:08:08,604
