59
00:09:14,867 --> 00:09:16,172
Merda!

60
00:09:20,831 --> 00:09:22,206
Newt, anda cá para cima!

61
00:09:22,207 --> 00:09:23,596
Estou quase.

62
00:09:32,926 --> 00:09:34,231
Newt, vai!

63
00:09:40,017 --> 00:09:41,989
